The species was not examined by author, the following description is from 
<bibRefCitation id="A2494B29221CE755FBA02023C4D51634" author="Medler" box="[1032,1206,1842,1868]" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" refString="Medler, J. T. (1992) Revision of the tribe Phyllyphantini in the Oriental Region, with descriptions of new genera and new species. Oriental Insects, 26, 1 - 38." type="journal article" year="1992">
